{"tid":957553,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"其實任天堂WII U先係PARTY GAME之最強者，聖誔新年拎出黎同朋友玩無一部可以比得上..!","createTime":"2018-12-27T06:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T08:14:24.000Z","uid":199235,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79b2f1d729d51644b4a4101097cbc126c07c5ff9","tid":957553,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得WII U 先係遊戲界最有創意既遊戲機<br />\n將坐埋一齊合家歡既PARTY GAME 創意升到極致, 暫時SWITCH都唔夠佢黎,<br />\n因為佢係一部傳統主機需要插電視, 但另一邊就好似SWITCH咁有個有一個6&quot;mon既GAME PAD同時玩, 互動性就可以無限放大, <br />\n先黎睇下以下呢隻GAME &amp; WARIO WII U 既遊戲影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kRBAad-vF7Q?t=455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkRBAad-vF7Q%3Ft%3D455&d=KPiejKE5eLK68LjQx65YECwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ff4bd565\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kRBAad-vF7Q?t=455</a><br />\n佢係模擬緊一個小朋友厘埋係房間偷打機但又唔可以比媽咪發現, 段片睇到你真係要拎主個GAME PAD手制玩WARIO (GBA個隻),  但電視又會不停SHOW 房間既情況要閃避, 又要玩GAME又要避阿媽突襲真係又好玩又好好笑, <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zxBi06ggX-g?t=975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzxBi06ggX-g%3Ft%3D975&d=KPiejKE5eLK68LjQx65YECwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2d404f99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zxBi06ggX-g?t=975</a><br />\n呢個遊戲係用GAME PAD對住電視影相, 要捕足獵物, 又係好有創意, <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aNvNbfsEodE?t=736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaNvNbfsEodE%3Ft%3D736&d=KPiejKE5eLK68LjQx65YECwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=97d0ae27\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aNvNbfsEodE?t=736</a><br />\n呢隻多人GAME個玩法又係勁過癮, 記住係用GAME PAD對住個MON 玩, 而唔係純用手制描方向...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xpLtJVcimec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxpLtJVcimec&d=KPiejKE5eLK68LjQx65YECwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=bc1ebc31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xpLtJVcimec</a><br />\n呢隻估賊仔遊戲, 做賊仔個位就要拎住個game pad 望住個MON仔係遊戲入面偷生果, 而其他人就望住大電視係度估邊個係賊, 呢個遊戲就算唔識打機都會覺得好好玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上只係wii u 其中一隻最hit既party game game &amp; wario既一小部份遊戲, 但只係齋睇已經好笑到飛起, 我只係覺得好可惜呢部咁有創意既遊戲機比較少人接觸, 好多人一提起任天堂只會講mario &amp; zelda, pokemon, 但唔知任天堂背後其實一直想將坐埋一齊打既群體遊戲發揮到最大創意, 可惜現今社會無輪時間同空間都唔容許, 但我都想比大家認識下wii u 係一部咩遊戲機, 亦覺得switch 取代唔到wii u, 作為真機迷, 及鍾意與朋友坐埋一齊打機既人仕, 我覺得wii u 點都要買番部係屋企看門口,<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下個post繼續討論wii u 既皇牌party game"},{"pid":"3226ead42d15beba7c0c72c16c59e23a9b685a9a","tid":957553,"uid":33523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"Mario Party 10 識玩一定係做 Bowser<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a0b1ad62a6f336c95dc524b208f5af36c81343","tid":957553,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3226ead42d15beba7c0c72c16c59e23a9b685a9a","tid":957553,"uid":33523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"Mario Party 10 識玩一定係做 Bowser<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"係, 無錯, 如果朋友當中有個係特別臭寸, 咁呢位就O岩佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4732276dade2e0fb29819febe0283ad8ab94fed","tid":957553,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6a0b1ad62a6f336c95dc524b208f5af36c81343","tid":957553,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3226ead42d15beba7c0c72c16c59e23a9b685a9a","tid":957553,"uid":33523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"Mario Party 10 識玩一定係做 Bowser<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:30:34.000Z","msg"